11
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:35,520
Aww...

12
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:37,650
She's so precious.

13
00:00:37,770 --> 00:00:39,860
Then one day
when I was about your age,

14
00:00:39,860 --> 00:00:43,440
I woke up to find
that a cutie mark had appeared.

15
00:00:43,490 --> 00:00:45,110
Pony:
Look at her hair!

16
00:00:45,110 --> 00:00:46,740
[ Laughter ]

17
00:00:46,780 --> 00:00:49,030
Yes, I know, but, honestly,

18
00:00:49,030 --> 00:00:51,870
that's how everypony was wearing
their mane back then.

19
00:00:51,950 --> 00:00:54,040
I had decided to become
a teacher,

20
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:56,080
and the flowers
symbolize my hope

21
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:58,630
That I could help
my future students bloom

22
00:00:58,710 --> 00:01:00,920
if I nurtured them
with knowledge.

23
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,550
The smiles represented
the cheer I hoped to bring

24
00:01:03,590 --> 00:01:05,800
to my little ponies
while they were learning.

25
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:09,640
Now, can anyone tell me when a
pony gets his or her cutie mark?

26
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,180
Oh! Oh! Oh!

27
00:01:11,220 --> 00:01:13,970
When she discovers
that certain something

28
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:15,640
that makes her special.

29
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,140
That's right, twist.

30
00:01:17,140 --> 00:01:19,940
A cutie mark
appears on a pony's flank

31
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,690
when he or she finds
that certain something

32
00:01:22,730 --> 00:01:25,110
that makes them different
from every other pony.

33
00:01:25,150 --> 00:01:26,070
Discovering
what makes you unique

34
00:01:26,110 --> 00:01:27,570
isn't something
that happens overnight.

35
00:01:27,570 --> 00:01:29,200
Psst!

36
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:31,990
And no amount of hoping,
wishing, or begging...
psst!

37
00:01:32,030 --> 00:01:34,620
...will make a cutie mark appear
before its time.

38
00:01:34,620 --> 00:01:36,580
Psst!

39
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:38,000
What?!

40
00:01:41,590 --> 00:01:44,000
Apple Bloom!

41
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,630
Are you passing a note?

42
00:01:45,670 --> 00:01:47,840
Uh...um...

43
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,180
What could be so important

44
00:01:49,180 --> 00:01:51,260
that it couldn't wait
until after class?

45
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:53,850
[ Gasps ]
It's blank.

46
00:01:53,850 --> 00:01:55,680
[ Laughs ]

47
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,680
Remind you
of anypony?

48
