will be there,

220
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:50,730
and they'll all have
their cutie marks,

221
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,950
and I want to get my
cutie mark, but I'm no
good at selling apples,

222
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:54,270
but I really
want to go to the party,

223
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:56,390
but how could I go to
the party if I don't
have my cutie mark,

224
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,290
which my big sister says
I'm gonna get eventually,

225
00:08:58,330 --> 00:09:01,650
